{"word":"G3670 - ὁμολογέω - homologéō - hom-ol-og-eh'-o - Con- fess","slug":"G3670","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>homologéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hom-ol-og-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Con- fess"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x0314;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - homologeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hom-ol-og-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G3674\">G3674</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>assent</i>, that is, <i>covenant</i>, <i>acknowledge:</i> - con- (pro-) fess, confession is made, give thanks, promise."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1843\">G1843</a>, <a href=\"#/G3671\">G3671</a>, <a href=\"#/G3672\">G3672</a>, <a href=\"#/G437\">G437</a>"}]}